37
00:02:45,042 --> 00:02:45,762
Today is his day off.

38
00:02:45,961 --> 00:02:46,801
Go talk some sense into him.

39
00:02:48,081 --> 00:02:49,561
I'm glad you're here, Ms. Xu.

40
00:02:50,042 --> 00:02:50,641
Better go check

41
