42
00:02:58,042 --> 00:02:58,641
Jin Shichuan!

43
00:03:02,602 --> 00:03:03,121
Let's go.

44
00:03:03,521 --> 00:03:04,162
Jin Shichuan!

45
00:03:05,202 --> 00:03:06,002
What happened?

46
