to stabilize first.

172
00:10:08,681 --> 00:10:09,922
But TC is currently...

173
00:10:09,922 --> 00:10:11,642
At the current stage, attempting

174
00:10:12,882 --> 00:10:13,841
to develop new markets

175
00:10:13,922 --> 00:10:14,561
is much too early.

176
00:10:14,961 --> 00:10:15,681
