177
00:10:18,362 --> 00:10:19,122
Yes, sir.

178
00:10:19,721 --> 00:10:21,122
TC made 20 percent of this quarter's profit

179
00:10:21,282 --> 00:10:22,201
for the group.

180
00:10:22,681 --> 00:10:23,362
