183
00:10:27,601 --> 00:10:29,201
Mr. Huo probably has his reasons.

184
00:10:29,601 --> 00:10:30,321
Like what?

185
00:10:31,601 --> 00:10:32,801
He must be wary about TC

186
00:10:33,002 --> 00:10:34,162
