201
00:11:19,162 --> 00:11:20,002
Did you two love rivals

202
00:11:20,201 --> 00:11:21,122
get into a fight?

203
00:11:23,242 --> 00:11:23,801
Almost.

204
00:11:24,162 --> 00:11:24,922
Seriously?

205
00:11:27,481 --> 00:11:28,441
